snippet.title: Smart Moves! | Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
#SmartMoves #XboxOne #TrixGaming
Overall Review: 9.0/10

Review:
Smart Moves is a strategy game that I could not put down while playing. A simple yet complex game forces you to make "smart moves" when trying to complete a level. Each move could be one step closer to your reward or even one step closer to you having to restart the level. A game I highly recommend playing.
